value:
FOR tds IN thermodatasets
    FILTER tds.properties.name == "SUPCRT98"
    FOR v IN 1..1 INBOUND tds pulls
        SORT v.properties.symbol
        RETURN { symbol: v.properties.symbol, name: v.properties.name, formula: v.properties.formula}
name: symbols-formulas

value:
FOR vertex IN @id;
FOR v,e  IN 1..3 INBOUND vertex
mixing, specific
FILTER v._label == 'interaction'
RETURN v._id
name: phase

value:
FOR tds IN thermodatasets
    FILTER tds.properties.symbol == "PSI-Nagra-12-07"
    FOR v IN 1..1 INBOUND tds pulls
        FILTER ["AUG20_GEMS:2001:dat:", "AUG20_GEMS:2001:dat:       ", "AUG20_GEMS:2001:dat:            ", "GEMS_AUG20:2001:dat:            "] ANY == v.properties.comment 
        SORT v.properties.symbol
        FOR r IN 1..1 INBOUND v defines
        RETURN { symbol: r.properties.symbol, formula: r.properties.equation}
name: datasources

value:
FOR tds IN thermodatasets
    FILTER tds.properties.symbol == "PSI-Nagra-12-07"
    FOR v IN 1..1 INBOUND tds basis
        FILTER CONTAINS(v, "CODATA")
        SORT v.properties.symbol
        RETURN v
name: elements
